ARSystem Password Decrypt
=========================

The action is able to decode an AR System password and to show the exact string value, to be validated in AR environment configurations.

The standard command line is described below:
areasy -action admin.password.decrypt -password <ARSystem password>

Where:
	-password = this is the ARSystem password that will be decoded to show the exact string value

Examples:
---------
1) areasy -runtime -action admin.password.decrypt -password "6r/4wTMluB+HGNI9iv5c8J1GAGUe6eEoB3lakjYtnUDSr4Ek8dEw/Ls/GKs6du6LiK1YqXx3mxcMKS1AAsaNsKjHEvQOakFUw3/RlQ3rmDInh+nXhocejQ=="
	= execute locally the transformation of the specified AR password into a clean string

2) areasy -action admin.password.decrypt -password "6r/4wTMluB+HGNI9iv5c8J1GAGUe6eEoB3lakjYtnUDSr4Ek8dEw/Ls/GKs6du6LiK1YqXx3mxcMKS1AAsaNsKjHEvQOakFUw3/RlQ3rmDInh+nXhocejQ=="
   	= execute on the ARSystem server the transformation of the specified AR password into a clean string
